  "instructions": [
    "Melt the butter in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the dry white wine and vinegar to the saucepan, stirring to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to a simmer and cook until the liquid has almost completely evaporated, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the grated Gruyère cheese and stir until melted and smooth.",
    "Add the heavy cream and stir to combine.",
    "Season the bisque with salt, black pepper, and a pinch of cayenne pepper.",
    "Cook the bisque over low heat until heated through, about 5 minutes.",
    "Ladle the bisque into bowls and garnish with chopped fresh chives and parsley.",
    "Serve immediately, with a dollop of sour cream and a sprinkle of paprika, if desired."
  ],
